summary: The caller wants to know if a distributor can supply products to their store in Tamil Nadu. The distributor is  ITC. The agent helps the caller by registering their request and assuring them that ITC can supply all the products they would need. The caller also inquires about cigarettes and the agent informs them that ITC is the distributor for all products related to cigarettes as well. The caller finally asks if the office for ITC is in Bangalore, but the agent informs them it is all over India.
speaker_a_summary: The caller is enquiring about a potential transfer for a Tamil language speaking person. They are also trying to get details for a dealer for a deep product for a shop owner. The shop owner is located at Sri Venkateswara Store in Erode. The caller is also trying to get the contact details for the office in Bangalore for a Mr. Jon.
speaker_b_summary: The caller is enquiring about supply for his store. The representative asks for the store's address, and the caller provides the following details: Venkateswara Store, 1132/8 Gala, Ramaswamy Plaza, Shankar Shankar Sir, Sangaringala A, Saranga Sar, Sankari Trichengodu, THIRUCHUNGODU. The representative asks for the PIN code, and the caller provides it. The representative says they will connect the caller with Trichengo, and they ask for the PIN code again to verify. The caller provides the number. The representative says they will make a direct supply request to the distributor, and they confirm the details for the supply with the caller. The caller asks about the details of the supply, and the representative says they will provide all the details, including pricing, discounts, and products. The caller asks if they can also supply cigarettes and IC, and the representative confirms they can supply all products. The caller provides their contact number, and the representative says they will register the request and the team will contact the caller to provide the details. The caller thanks the representative and ends the call.
cohere_points:
- Customer is calling in to make a request for a product distribution supply for his store in Tamil
- They are asked for details of the store and the products they are looking for and informed of the registration process
- The caller is also asked for their contact details for the registration to be completed and they give their name as John. 
- The call ends with a thank you from both parties. 
- Key phrases: product distribution, supply, registration, contact details, company name.
